text: Ærest on easthealfe, of eastan wylles heafde, andlang lace to mylenburnan, thonne andlang streames oth gifle.
Thonne eft andlang streames oth ænnan pol thanon andlang lace oththa ealdan dic, thonne andlang dic oth hloscumbes heafud.
Thanon on ecge, andlang ecge oththa dic thanon andlang dic, oth ecgulfes treow, thanon east to ættandene middeweardre andlang dene eft to ættan wylle.
